ipxLinkConfTable.name: ipxLinkConfTable

ipxLinkConfRoutingProtocol.name: ipxLinkConfRoutingProtocol

ipxLinkConfNumbered.name: ipxLinkConfNumbered
ipxLinkConfNumbered.description: Determines if a WAN link is numbered.

ipxLinkConfNet.name: ipxLinkConfNet
